snippet.title: Resident Evil Village Cloud - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Resident Evil Village Cloud, the eighth main installment in the Resident Evil series, releases on Nintendo Switch on Oct. 28!
The Winters' Expansion pack, which includes Third Person Mode and new Story DLC, is also planned for release on Dec.2nd!

https://www.residentevil.com/switch/cloud/
